Lihis 2013

Lihis, director Joel Lamangan's entry to the 2013 Sineng Pambansa All Masters Series Film Festival, released its extended trailer on Monday, giving the public a peeek into the story of two male communist rebels who fell in love with each other despite discouragement from the people around them.

Set in the 70's during the darkest hours of Philippine History, we follow the story of two young NPA warriors who find themselves entangled in a web of frustration, despair and victory as they fight not only for democracy but also their love for each other.
